                    </div>
                    <span>If you use API's, or want to use API's, then I suggest getting this book. There are so many API calls out there, that no book contains them all. <P>This book helps you solve the API so you can use them in your applications. Definately a "must have" for any programmer out there worth his salt.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">It is a useful book in programming</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
